com.wedriveu.services.vehicle.rabbitmq

Interface Messages.NearestControl

  • Enclosing interface:
    Messages

    public static interface Messages.NearestControl
    Addresses used by the Messages.NearestControl Verticle to handle the requests used at the beginning of vehicle election process.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static java.lang.String AVAILABLE_REQUEST
      The address used by a NearestConsumerVerticle boundary to communicate a UserRequest received.
      static java.lang.String DATA_TO_VEHICLE
      The address used by a Messages.NearestControl to communicate to a VehicleFinderVerticle to start the find process.
      static java.lang.String GET_VEHICLE_NEAREST
      The address used by a Messages.NearestControl to communicate to a VehicleStoreImpl to fetch the Constants.Vehicle elected.
